### 添加阿里云OSS配置
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/configs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Aliyun OSS Test",
    "provider": "aliyun",
    "access_key": "YOUR_ALIYUN_ACCESS_KEY",
    "secret_key": "YOUR_ALIYUN_SECRET_KEY",
    "bucket": "your-bucket-name",
    "endpoint": "oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com",
    "region": "cn-beijing",
    "path_prefix": "",
    "storage_type": "standard"
}

### 获取所有OSS配置
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/configs

### 激活OSS配置（替换{configId}为实际ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/configs/{configId}/activate

### 获取单个OSS配置
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/configs/{configId}

### 更新OSS配置
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/configs/{configId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Aliyun OSS",
    "provider": "aliyun",
    "access_key": "YOUR_ALIYUN_ACCESS_KEY",
    "secret_key": "YOUR_ALIYUN_SECRET_KEY",
    "bucket": "your-bucket-name",
    "endpoint": "oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com",
    "region": "cn-beijing",
    "path_prefix": "uploads/",
    "storage_type": "standard"
}

### 删除OSS配置
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/configs/{configId}

### 测试OSS连接
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/oss/test-connection

### 上传文件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/files/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a test file content.
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 下载文件
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/files/download/test.txt

### 获取文件列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/files

### 删除文件
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/files/test.txt

### 同步文件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/files/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "local_path": "/path/to/local/directory",
    "remote_path": "remote/directory/",
    "sync_type": "upload"
}